@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fthjgk(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.cos(0.12) + wp.cos((tmp + 0.37 - v2 + 0.22)))
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.cos(tmp + 0.86) + wp.cos(v0 + 0.04)))
    tmp = wp.sin((wp.abs(tmp + 0.79) - v1))
    v2 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
